	Annotations: bim:Definition "Declares that the object is positioned upstream of another object (counterflow direction). Property designed to order elements of flows and pipes."@en
	Characteristics: Transitive
	Characteristics: Asymmetric
	InverseOf: bim:é.a.jusante.de

